name: FireLookup
0:
”Alexa, open fire lookup.”
”Alexa, ask fire lookup where is the nearest fire.”
”Alexa, ask fire lookup about the closest fire.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fire lookup
des: This skill will search through current fire data from the US National Interagency Fire Center, and report back information on the nearest uncontained fire to your location.
